body_html: Sorry, it was my mistake or rather the README was the issue. I had to give the same command line with "--size=256 --num_layers=2" during --decode too. Otherwise, it is looking for Cell3 which is non existent (and looks like default is that).

body: Sorry, it was my mistake or rather the README was the issue. I had to give the same command line with "--size=256 --num_layers=2" during --decode too. Otherwise, it is looking for Cell3 which is non existent (and looks like default is that).
